2:T6e8,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is AIVA better than Udio?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. AIVA scores 7.0 overall while Udio scores 8.0. AIVA is best for film and game composers and orchestral and classical music, while Udio excels for musicians exploring AI composition and high-quality AI music."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, AIVA or Udio?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"AIVA starts at $11/mo and Udio starts at $8/mo. AIVA offers a free plan. Udio offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from AIVA to Udio?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both AIVA and Udio support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about AIVA vs Udio?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, AIVA holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Udio has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise AIVA for excellent orchestral compositions and Udio for excellent audio quality."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, AIVA or Udio?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Udio for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, AIVA remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize excellent orchestral compositions. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$"